<h1>Details of This Task</h1>

<ul>
  <li>To-do ID#: <%= @got_todo['id'] %></li>
  <li>Name: <%= @got_todo['todo'] %></li>
  <li>Title: <%= @got_todo['note'] %></li>
  <li>Done? <%= if @got_todo['status'] ='t'; "Yes"; else "No"; end %></li>
  <li>Assigned to: <%= @assignee %></li>
  <li>Related to: Movie "<%= @for_movie %>"</li>
</ul>

Actions you can take:<br>
<a href="/todos/edit/<%= @got_todo['id'] %>"><button>Edit This Task</button></a><br>

<form action="/todos/delete/<%= @got_todo['id'] %>" method="post">
  <button>Delete This Todo</button><br>
</form>

<a href="/todos"><button>Go Back to All Tasks</button></a>










